{"tid":492900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"感覺到女朋友內心慶過火屎","createTime":"2017-12-08T03:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:30:31.000Z","uid":50351,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8971d83b080a4e6af306ea8a5885a95a159fc8","tid":492900,"uid":50351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"女朋友有家姐有細妹<br />\n家姐同佢唔似樣 好易分，但細妹同佢好似，只係肥少少同瘦少少既差別<br />\n<br />\n而佢全家女人都係鍾意著件長過條褲既t shirt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇落都無著褲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁緊係次次都起機架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日上左佢屋企食飯，我女朋友入左房換衫，之後有人出左黎，衣著同我女朋友平時屋企打扮一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望住對白滑雙腿，我即刻起到硬彬彬，黎左個緊密既back hug頂撚住佢屎忽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到喱度大家都知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女朋友望到應一應，但佢細妹又無咩反應，只係點頭話唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喱兩日女朋友都笑得好詭異，又溫馴左勁多<br />\n但我好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9210bd8c11c5167cb57eec3858693b80bfcd8f5","tid":492900,"uid":148779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"玩 3p lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e66a727469a73af4ec8cce0e655e8214a300d07","tid":492900,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"夜晚帶返個貞操帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係賓周仔都冇埋"},{"pid":"ff312eea890b47963639688f0e6d5ae032b3db2e","tid":492900,"uid":8762,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"可能呢幾日同你笑笑口個個係細妹...........你女友呢幾日扮你細妹出左去happy呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/